414
00:31:19,353 --> 00:31:20,605
Not much.

415
00:31:23,260 --> 00:31:24,875
What do you think, Webber?
Oh?

416
00:31:25,362 --> 00:31:27,649
You're boats-mate.
You know how it is out there.

417
00:31:27,651 --> 00:31:31,351
Now look, nobodys goin' over the bar
in this weather, Mr.Cluff. Nobody.

418
